me réveiller. Je suis sérieuse.

38
00:04:13,278 --> 00:04:15,658
D'accord

39
00:04:21,564 --> 00:04:23,883
Je t'aime tellement.

40
00:04:24,053 --> 00:04:26,234
Est ce que tu m'aimes ?

41
00:04:28,198 --> 00:04:30,606
Tu es ma vie, George.

42
00:04:30,691 --> 00:04:33,400
